e are trying to figure this out, but the pessimistic side of me is saying t=
he number of bundled TV customers will not drop to zero. We always thought =
the floor was 50 million, but that is tied in with the idea that people wil=
l work together to create a more efficient bundle.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"mar=
gin:0;"><br/>Something that John Malone said to us, about two months ago, w=
